pan><hr size=1>    I saw on Malignant's homepage that Yuri the high level mage of Sullon was jumped and slain by Malignant.  Sounded rather lame that Yuri didn't put up much of a fight.  Obviously someone has a lot to learn about P v P.<br>
<br>
 Anyone know more about the fight and what level the chars were that took him down?   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ushikakuthegorotsuki.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shikaku the Gorotsuki</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/26/01 12:12:09 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Yuri killed</span><hr size=1> I heard the same.. I'd bet money he was A.F.K. and forgot to turn the tag on.. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Yuri is too good at PvE to suck that bad at PvP..  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukelthana.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kelthana</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/26/01 12:22:34 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Yuri killed</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Yuri is too good at PvE to suck that bad at PvP<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
I would imagine the exact opposite to be true - if someone has spent all of their time on a PvP server trying to gain xp as fast as possible in PvE situations, they haven't been honing any PvP skills. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ushikakuthegorotsuki.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shikaku the Gorotsuki</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/26/01 1:24:01 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Yuri killed</span><hr size=1> I'm extremely good at PvP.. I take down any class I fight 1 on 1 as my Bard on Sullon.. but yet I cant do much PvE.. I'm not good at Solo on PvE.. then again, I'm a bard. But.. I think PvE is a lot more challenging than PvP... I came to Sullon.. I just PvP like I PvE.. Selo's, Magic Resist(With Poison/disease or cold/heat depending on casting foe.. if no caster, no song), De-haste song if fighting a pure melee class, twist AoE(DDD) and Bellow if drawn into melee combat.. ensures I do more damage than them.. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  But I cant pull that on PvE.. PvE mobs are smarter than PCs.. lol.. no offense. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukambic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kambic</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/26/01 5:40:55 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.theglobe.com/Kambic/TRINITY.GIF WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Yuri killed</span><hr size=1> I think it was a matter of about 20 people rushed him, and he didn't have a damage shield on, and last I checked, mages don't get any AE spells.<br>
<br>
 <p><a href="http://pub70.ezboard.com/bscreamspvp"><img src="http://members.theglobe.com/kambic/sig/joyous.gif"></a></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukelthana.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kelthana</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/26/01 5:54:59 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Yuri killed</span><hr size=1> Mages have both PBAEs and rains. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukambic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kambic</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/26/01 6:09:25 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.theglobe.com/Kambic/TRINITY.GIF WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Yuri killed</span><hr size=1> Really? Is there a limit to how many things it can hit?<br>
<br>
(I have never played a mage.. no, I mean, never, I think I made one once and I might have gotten level 2...) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unefertitz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Neferti TZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/26/01 6:13:24 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Yuri killed</span><hr size=1> Nope no limit on PBAE.<br>
